snippet.title: WWE Undefeated Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
WWE Undefeated, the latest WWE mobile game featuring real-time head-to-head competition, is coming on December 3, 2020, worldwide to iOS and Android devices. WWE Undefeated presents quick-session matches that blend over-the-top arcade-style action with real-time strategy gameplay.

Pre-register now to unlock AJ Styles: https://www.wweundefeated.com

Join the #wweundefeated conversation:
Facebook (https://www.facebook.com/WWEUndefeated)
Twitter (http://twitter.com/WWEUndefeated)
Instagram (https://www.instagram.com/WWEUndefeated/)
Discord (https://discord.gg/6E8Srnh)
